{"version":1,"entries":{"movie_1140498_detail_vi-VN":{"at":1774721245508,"data":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/bcw0QrKe9cM7MbjypxMPFdT6hrM.jpg","belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[{"id":35,"name":"Phim Hài"},{"id":18,"name":"Phim Chính Kịch"}],"homepage":"","id":1140498,"imdb_id":"tt28083456","origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_title":"Is This Thing On?","overview":"Khi cuộc hôn nhân tan vỡ, Alex đối mặt với tuổi trung niên và ly hôn, tìm kiếm mục đích sống mới trong làng hài kịch New York. Trong khi đó, vợ anh, Tess, phải đối mặt với những hy sinh vì gia đình, buộc họ phải cùng nhau nuôi dạy con cái và tìm kiếm bản sắc riêng...","popularity":9.1276,"poster_path":"/YD6QzcokTMe3EViM0hLbNCxf4y.jpg","production_companies":[{"id":127929,"logo_path":"/7DLKyL15ETI9645XSr9JcbMV79c.png","name":"Searchlight Pictures","origin_country":"US"},{"id":85823,"logo_path":"/vX3emcjqjXse76NAUZikSIzHH4t.png","name":"Archery Pictures","origin_country":"GB"},{"id":201152,"logo_path":null,"name":"Lea Pictures","origin_country":"US"},{"id":22213,"logo_path":"/qx9K6bFWJupwde0xQDwOvXkOaL8.png","name":"TSG Entertainment","origin_country":"US"}],"production_countries":[{"iso_3166_1":"GB","name":"United Kingdom"},{"iso_3166_1":"US","name":"United States of America"}],"release_date":"2025-12-19","revenue":866747,"runtime":121,"spoken_languages":[{"english_name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English"}],"status":"Released","tagline":"","title":"Ai Còn Lắng Nghe?","video":false,"vote_average":6.552,"vote_count":86}},"person_8785_translations":{"at":1774721246365,"data":{"id":8785,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Ciarán Hinds (/ˈkɪərən/ KEER-ən; born 9 February 1953) is an Irish actor from Belfast, Northern Ireland. Hinds is known for a range of screen and stage roles. He has starred in feature films including The Cook, the Thief, His Wife & Her Lover (1989), Persuasion (1995), Oscar and Lucinda (1997), Road to Perdition (2002), The Sum of All Fears (2002), Munich (2005), Amazing Grace (2007), There Will Be Blood (2007), Miss Pettigrew Lives for a Day (2008), Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows – Part 2 (2011), Tinker Tailor Soldier Spy (2011), Silence (2016), First Man (2018) and Belfast (2021), the last of which earned him Oscar and BAFTA nominations for Best Supporting Actor.\n\nKnown for his distinctively deep voice, Hinds is also known for his voice role as Grand Pabbie, the Troll King, in the animated films Frozen (2013) and  Frozen II (2019). He played General Zakharow in Red Sparrow (2018). He also portrayed Steppenwolf in Zack Snyder's Justice League (2017) and its 2021 director's cut. \n\nHis television roles include Julius Caesar in the series Rome, DCI James Langton in Above Suspicion, Mance Rayder in Game of Thrones, and Captain Sir John Franklin in The Terror. In addition, Hinds appeared in season 3 of Shetland (2016), produced by ITV.\n\nAs a stage actor, Hinds has spent periods with the Royal Shakespeare Company and the Royal National Theatre, and six seasons with Glasgow Citizens' Theatre. Hinds has continued to work on stage throughout his career. In 2020, he was ranked 31st on The Irish Times list of Ireland's greatest film actors.\n\nDescription above from the Wikipedia article Ciarán Hinds, licensed under CC-BY-SA, full list of contributors on Wikipedia.","name":"Ciarán Hinds","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Киаран Хайндс","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"Ciarán Hinds (* 9. Februar 1953 in Belfast, Nordirland, Vereinigtes Königreich) ist ein aus Nordirland stammender irischer Schauspieler.  1981 begann mit Excalibur seine Karriere beim Film, worauf einige Film- und Fernsehrollen folgten. So spielte er einen Mossad-Agenten in Steven Spielbergs Film München, Aberforth Dumbledore im letzten Teil der Harry-Potter-Filme, einen irischen Gangster in Road to Perdition, den russischen Präsidenten in Der Anschlag sowie Julius Caesar in der HBO-Fernsehserie Rome. Ab 2013 war Hinds bis 2015 wiederkehrend in der mehrfach ausgezeichneten HBO-Fernsehserie Game of Thrones als King Beyond the Wall, Mance Rayder, zu sehen.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"PL","iso_639_1":"pl","name":"Polski","english_name":"Polish","data":{"biography":"Ciarán Hinds urodził się w Belfaście, stolicy hrabstwa Antrim i największym mieście Irlandii Północnej (Wielka Brytania). Jest najmłodszy z pięciorga rodzeństwa, ma cztery siostry. Jego ojciec był lekarzem. Miał nadzieję, że jedyny syn pójdzie w jego ślady, ale tak się nie stało. Matka Moya, zajmująca się aktorstwem amatorsko, wywarła największy wpływ na jego decyzję, aby również zająć się tym zawodem. Chociaż zaczął studiować prawo na Queen's University w Belfaście, opuścił uczelnię i podjął studia aktorskie na Royal Academy Of Dramatic Art w Londynie (Anglia, Wielka Brytania).\n\nRozpoczął karierę sceniczną przy Glasgow Citizens' Theater (Szkocja, Wielka Brytania) w przedstawieniu \"Kopciuszek\". Przez kilka lat grał główne role w spektaklach \"Arszenik i stare koronki\" oraz \"Faust\". Współpracował z The Field Day Theatre Company. Przyłączył się również do The Royal Shakespeare Company, podróżując z nimi dookoła świata i grając główną rolę w przedstawieniu \"Ryszard III\".\n\nNa kinowym ekranie zadebiutował w 1981 roku (film \"Excalibur\"), grając z takimi aktorami jak Liam Neeson, Gabriel Byrne i Patrick Stewart. Pojawił się  też w wielu produkcjach telewizyjnych. Grał klasyczne charaktery jak Edward Rochester w telewizyjnym dramacie romantycznym \"Dziwne losy Jane Eyre\"  i kapitan Wentworth w melodramacie \"Perswazje\".  Pilnie strzeże swojego życia prywatnego. Od wielu lat jest związany z francusko-wietnamską aktorką Hélène Patarot. Mają córkę Aoife (irlandzki odpowiednik imienia Ewa). Mieszkają w Londynie.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"키어런 하인즈","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CZ","iso_639_1":"cs","name":"Český","english_name":"Czech","data":{"biography":"Ciarán Hinds (narozen 9. února 1953) je irský herec. Jako všestranný charakterní herec se objevil v celovečerních filmech jako Nejhorší obavy, Road to Perdition, Mnichov, Až na krev, Harry Potter a Relikvie smrti – část 2, Žena v černém, Jeden musí z kola ven, Ledové království, Mlčení, Rudá volavka, Liga spravedlnosti, První člověk a Ledové království II.\n\nMezi jeho televizní role patří Gaius Julius Caesar v seriálu Řím, vrchní inspektor James Langton v seriálu Nad podezřením a Mance Rayder v seriálu Hra o trůny. Jako divadelní herec má za sebou angažmá v Royal Shakespeare Company, Royal National Theatre v Londýně a šest sezón v Glasgow Citizens' Theatre a v práci na divadelních prknech pokračuje po celou dobu své kariéry.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"塞伦·希德（Ciarán Hinds，1953年2月9日-），爱尔兰演员。作为一名多才多艺的角色演员，他曾出演过故事片，如《所有恐惧的总和》、《灭亡之路》、《慕尼黑》、《血色将至》、《哈利波特与死亡圣器 第2部分》、《修补匠裁缝士兵间谍》、《冰雪奇缘》、《沉默》、《红麻雀》、《正义联盟》、《第一人》和《冰雪奇缘II》。\n\n他的电视角色包括《罗马》系列中的盖乌斯·朱利叶斯·凯撒、《怀疑之上》中的DCI詹姆斯·兰顿和《权力的游戏》中的曼斯·雷德。作为一名舞台演员，海因兹曾在皇家莎士比亚剧团、伦敦皇家国家剧院和格拉斯哥市民剧院工作过六个赛季，在他的整个职业生涯中，他一直在舞台上工作。","name":"塞伦·希德","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IR","iso_639_1":"fa","name":"فارسی","english_name":"Persian","data":{"biography":"","name":"کیران هایندز","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Кіаран Гайндс","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"SA","iso_639_1":"ar","name":"العربية","english_name":"Arabic","data":{"biography":"","name":"كيران هايندز","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"塞倫·希德（1953 年 2 月 9 日-），愛爾蘭演員。作為一名多才多藝的角色演員，他曾出演過故事片，如《所有恐懼的總和》、《滅亡之路》、《慕尼黑》、《黑金風雲》、《哈利波特與死亡聖器——第 2 部分》、《諜網謎蹤》、《魔雪奇緣》、《沉默》、《紅麻雀》、《正義聯盟》、《第一人》和《冰雪奇緣 II》。\n\n他的電視角色包括《羅馬》系列中的蓋烏斯·朱利葉斯·凱撒、《懷疑之上》中的 DCI 詹姆斯·蘭頓和《權力的遊戲》中的曼斯·雷德。作為一名舞台演員，海因茲曾在皇家莎士比亞劇團、倫敦皇家國家劇院和格拉斯哥市民劇院工作過六個賽季，在他的整個職業生涯中，他一直在舞台上工作。","name":"塞倫·希德","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TR","iso_639_1":"tr","name":"Türkçe","english_name":"Turkish","data":{"biography":"Ciarán Hinds, 9 Şubat 1953 tarihinde Belfast, Kuzey İrlanda'da dünyaya gelmiştir. Bir doktor baba ve amatör tiyatrocu bir öğretmenin oğlu olan Hinds, sanatla iç içe, Katolik bir ailede büyüdü. Başlangıçta babasının izinden giderek Queen's University Belfast'ta hukuk eğitimi almaya başlasa da, tiyatroya olan tutkusu ağır bastı ve eğitimini yarıda bırakarak Londra'daki prestijli Kraliyet Dramatik Sanatlar Akademisi'ne (RADA) kaydoldu. Profesyonel kariyerine Glasgow Citizens Theatre'da adım atan Hinds, burada klasik tiyatro eserlerinde uzun yıllar sahne alarak oyunculuk tekniğini mükemmelleştirdi. Peter Brook'un efsanevi \"The Mahabharata\" (1989) dünya turnesinde yer alarak uluslararası tiyatro camiasında saygınlık kazandı.\n\nSinema dünyasına girişi, John Boorman'ın epik fantezi filmi \"Excalibur\" (1981) ile oldu. Ancak geniş kitlelerce tanınmasını sağlayan ilk önemli rolü, Jane Austen uyarlaması \"İkna\" (Persuasion) (1995) filmindeki Kaptan Wentworth performansıydı. Bu rol, onun romantik ve dramatik derinliğini sergilemesine olanak tanıdı. Hinds, kariyeri boyunca hem Hollywood'un büyük bütçeli yapımlarında hem de bağımsız sanat filmlerinde \"karakter oyuncusu\" olarak vazgeçilmez bir isim haline geldi. Steven Spielberg'ün \"Münih\" (Munich) (2005), Michael Mann'in \"Miami Vice\" (2006) ve Paul Thomas Anderson'ın \"Kan Dökülecek\" (There Will Be Blood) (2007) gibi yönetmen sinemasının önemli örneklerinde kilit roller üstlendi.\n\nHinds'in kariyerindeki en ikonik performanslardan biri, HBO'nun kült tarihi dizisi \"Rome\" (2005-2007) oldu. Burada canlandırdığı Gaius Julius Caesar karakteri, otoriter duruşu ve karizmasıyla televizyon tarihinin en başarılı Sezar yorumlarından biri olarak kabul edildi. Fantastik dünyalara da yabancı olmayan oyuncu, \"Harry Potter ve Ölüm Yadigarları: Bölüm 2\" (2011) filminde Aberforth Dumbledore'u ve \"Game of Thrones\" (2013-2015) dizisinde Duvarın Ötesindeki Kral Mance Rayder'ı canlandırdı. Ayrıca DC Genişletilmiş Evreni'nde (DCEU) \"Justice League\" (2017) ve özellikle karakterin derinleştiği \"Zack Snyder's Justice League\" (2021) versiyonunda, baş kötü karakter Steppenwolf'a hareket yakalama (motion capture) teknolojisiyle hayat verdi.\n\nKariyerinin zirve noktalarından birini yakın dönemde, hemşehrisi Kenneth Branagh'ın yönettiği yarı otobiyografik film \"Belfast\" (2021) ile yaşadı. Bu filmde canlandırdığı şefkatli ve bilge büyükbaba \"Pop\" rolü, ona En İyi Yardımcı Erkek Oyuncu dalında Akademi Ödülü (Oscar) adaylığı getirdi. Tiyatro köklerinden asla kopmayan ve sinemada yetkinliğini kanıtlayan Hinds, son olarak \"The Lord of the Rings: The Rings of Power\" (2024) dizisinin ikinci sezonunda gizemli Karanlık Büyücü rolüyle izleyici karşısına çıkmıştır.","name":"","primary":false}}]}},"movie_1465986_credits":{"at":1774721248497,"data":{"id":1465986,"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":1595615,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Kelsey Pribilski","original_name":"Kelsey Pribilski","popularity":0.3731,"profile_path":"/kD9tlNx7FVe91VXA3YInWvF9LeR.jpg","cast_id":27,"character":"Lynn Page","credit_id":"681101df2137f34c24ead498","order":0},{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":2547272,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"William Magnuson","original_name":"William Magnuson","popularity":0.2053,"profile_path":"/h3pya0jLFzukfoVnC35O8qNAtc7.jpg","cast_id":19,"character":"Lucas Page","credit_id":"6800cd2ff39c730125d9533d","order":1},{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":1155596,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"John Gholson","original_name":"John Gholson","popularity":0.3546,"p